text: Martin Tichý (born 13 July 1968) is a Czech rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Czechoslovakia Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:People from Mělník District
